<h1> Hotfix 0.9.1

## A small hotfix to change & fix some stuff.

---

# Front-end

> ### Commands

- Fluff, Drink, Hug, Pat, Sleep, Smile, Step
    - Rate-limit has been decreased from 2 > 1 Second

- Boop, Snack
    - Rate-limit has been removed.
